Mr Chavez -- who is 58 -- has now had four operations since he was first taken ill in June last year.
The exact nature of his cancer has never been made public. President Rafael Correa of Ecuador -- a close ally of Mr Chavez -- has said his revolutionary programme must continue even if he is not able to return to power.
Pemerintah Venezuela mengatakan Presiden Hugo Chavez dalam keadaan stabil setelah menjalani operasi kanker di Kuba, hari Selasa.
Namun para menteri mengatakan pemulihannya akan berjalan rumit dan memperingatkan rakyat Venezuela untuk bersiap menghadapi masa-masa sulit kedepan.
