Congolese athletes go missing in London
Atlet Kongo hilang di London
Three killed in Texas shooting incident
Tiga tewas dalam penembakan di Texas

Media reports in the Democratic Republic of Congo say four members of the country's Olympic delegation have gone missing in London.
The UN-sponsored Radio Okapi said the judo player, Cedric Mandembo, disappeared from the Olympic village in London shortly after the closing ceremony.
He had been defeated within 49 seconds in his only judo bout at the Games. A Congolese judo coach, a boxing coach, and the athletics technical director are also reported missing. The authorities in London are looking for at least seven Olympic athletes from Cameroon.
Five of them -- all male boxers -- told the BBC that they had left after being threatened by senior members of the Cameroon Olympic delegation that their careers would be over if they lost their bouts.
The Cameroonian authorities have denied that the athletes were ill-treated.
Sejumlah laporan media di Republik Demokratik Kongo menyebutkan empat anggota delegasi Olimpiade negara itu hilang di London.
Radio Okapi yang disponsori PBB menyebutkan atlet judo, Cadric Mandembo, hilang dari perkampungan atlet Olimpiade di London tidak lama setelah upacara penutupan.
Ia dikalahkan hanya dalam waktu 49 detik pada satu-satunya pertandingan judo yang ia ikuti.
Pelatih judo, tinju dan direktur teknis atletik juga dilaporkan hilang. Pihak berwenang di London juga tengah melacak paling tidak tujuh atlet dari Kamerun.
Lima di antara mereka adalah atlet tinju putra. Mereka mengatakan kepada BBC mereka menghilang setelah diancam oleh anggota senior delegasi Olimpiade Kamerun bahwa karir mereka akan selesai bila mereka kalah.
Pemerintah Kamerun menyanggah atlet mereka diperlakukan secara tidak baik.

Police in the United States say three people have been killed in a shooting incident near a Texas university campus, including the alleged gunman. 
One of the dead was the first police officer to arrive on the scene. The suspect, who was wounded during an exchange of gunfire, was taken into custody but later died of his injuries.
The shooting was close to A&amp;M University, northwest of Houston.
Polisi di Amerika Serikat mengatakan tiga orang tewas dalam insiden penembakan di dekat kampus universitas Texas, termasuk penembak.
Salah seorang korban tewas adalah polisi yang pertama datang ke tempat kejadian.
Tersangka, yang terluka dalam baku tembak, ditahan namun kemudian meninggal karena luka-lukanya. Penembakan itu terjadi di dekat Universitas A&amp;M di barat laut Houston.
