Volcano erupts in New Zealand
Gunung berapi meletus di Selandia Baru
Munich massacre widow denounces IOC
Janda pembantaian Munich mengecam IOC

A volcano has erupted in New Zealand, disrupting flights, closing roads and causing nearby residents to leave their homes.
Rocks and flames poured out of Mount Tongariro, on North Island, for 30 minutes, sending a cloud of ash more than 6.000 metres into the air.
Civil defence officials in New Zealnd said they'd had no reports of any injuries or damage to property. The eruption was the first significant activity from the volcano for 115 tahun.
Gunung berapi meleutus di Selandia Baru dan menyebabkan penerbangan terganggu, jalan-jalan ditutup dan penduduk yang tinggal di sekitar mengungsi.
Gunung Tongariro, di North Island, memuntahkan batu dan api selama 30 menit, dan menyemburkan abu setinggi lebih dari 6.000 meter ke udara.
Para pejabat pertahanan sipil di Selandia Baru mengatakan tidak ada laporan tentang korban luka, atau kerusakan bangunan. Letusan itu adalah yang pertama dalam waktu 115 tahun.

The widow of one of the eleven Israeli athletes murdered at the Munich Olympics in 1972 has denounced the International Olympic Committee for refusing to hold a minute's silence in their memory at the start of every Games.
Ankie Spitzer was loudly applauded at a ceremony in London when she turned to the IOC president, Jacques Rogge, and accused him of forgetting eleven members of the Olympic family.
The British prime minister, David Cameron, said the killings -- after the athletes were taken hostage by Palestinian militants -- had been a shocking act of evil.
Janda salah seorang korban dari 11 atlet Israel yang tewas dalam Olimpiade Munich 1972 mengecam Komite Olimpiade Internasional karena menolak melakukan hening cipta untuk mengenang korban setiap awal pertandingan.
Ankie Spitzer disambut dalam upacara di London saat ia menunjuk ke presiden IOC, Jacques Rogge dan menuduhnya lupa atas 11 anggota keluarga Olimpiade itu.
Perdadana Menteri Inggris, David Cameron, mengatakan pembunuhan -yang terjadi setelah atlet itu diculik oleh militan Palestina- merupakan tindakan setan yang mengejutkan.
