Fukushima radioactivity in California tuna
Radioaktif Fukushima ditemukan di tuna California

NATO said al-Taifi commanded foreign insurgents in Afghanistan. 
NATO-led forces in Afghanistan say they've killed one of al-Qaeda's most influential figures in the country.
In a statement, they described Sakhr al-Taifi as al-Qaeda's second most senior leader in Afghanistan.
They said he commanded foreign insurgents and directed attacks against coalition and Afghan forces.
He was killed late on Sunday in an air strike in Kunar Province.
Pasukan pimpinan NATO di Afghanistan mengatakan mereka menewaskan salah satu tokoh al-Qaida paling berpengaruh di negara tersebut.
Dalam satu pernyataan, mereka menggambarkan Sakhr al-Taifi sebagai pemimpin paling senior kedua al-Qaida di Afghanistan.
