Whitney Houston's body flown home
Jenazah Whitney Houston diterbangkan pulang
Berita pertama mengenai pernyataan India terkait serangan bom hari Senin dan berita kedua tentang rencana pemakaman Whitney Houston.

India's Home Minister, Palaniappan Chidambaram, says the person who carried out a bomb attack on Monday, targeting an Israeli diplomat, was "very well-trained".
An Israeli embassy official, her driver and two passers-by were injured when a bomb wrecked their car in Delhi.
Mr Chidambaram told reporters that apparently a motorcyclist approached from behind and attached an explosive device to the car's rear door.
Israeli officials defused a second car bomb in the Georgian capital, Tbilisi.
The Israeli prime minister, Benjamin Netanyahu, has blamed Iran and its allies in the Lebanese militant group Hezbollah for the attacks. Iran denies involvement.
Menteri Dalam Negeri India Palaniappan Chidambaram mengatakan pelaku pengeboman hari Senin dengan sasaran seorang diplomat Israel, "sangat terlatih".
Seorang pejabat kedutaan Israel, sopir dan dua warga yang kebetulan berada di tempat kejadian mengalami luka-luka ketika ledakan bom menghancurkan mobil mereka di Delhi.
Kepada para wartawan Chidambaram mengatakan tampaknya seorang pengendara sepede motor mendekat dari belakang dan menempatkan alat peledak di pintu mobil belakang.
Para pejabat Israel menjinakkan bom kedua di ibukota Georgia, Tbilisi.
Perdana Menteri Israel Benjamin Netanyahu menuding Iran dan sekutu-sekutunya di kelompok militan Lebanon, Hizbullah, atas serangan-serangan. Iran menyatakan tidak terlibat.

The body of the American popstar, Whitney Houston, has been taken from California to her home state of New Jersey, where her funeral is expected to take place later this week.
Whitney Houston was found submerged and unconscious on Saturday in a bath at a hotel in Beverly Hills.
The authorities say toxicology tests are underway but it may be several weeks before they can confirm the cause of the singer's death.
Jenazah bintang pop Amerika Serikat, Whitney Houston, dibawa dari California ke negara bagian asalnya, New Jersey, tempat Whitney Houston rencananya akan dimakamkan akhir pekan nanti.
Whitney Houston ditemukan dalam keadaan terendam dan pingsan di dalam bak mandi di sebuah hotel Beverly Hills pada hari Sabtu.
Pihak berwenang mengatakan pemeriksaan kandungan racun dalam tubuh sedang dilakukan tetapi mungkin diperlukan waktu berminggu-minggu sebelum diketahui penyebab kematian penyanyi itu.
